graph TB
    subgraph "CodeFlare Operator"
        Manager[Operator Manager<br/>Deployment]
        Controller[RayCluster Controller<br/>Reconciler]
        MutatingWebhook[Mutating Webhook<br/>Port 9443/TCP]
        ValidatingWebhook[Validating Webhook<br/>Port 9443/TCP]
        CertController[Certificate Controller]
        Metrics[Metrics Endpoint<br/>Port 8080/TCP]
        Health[Health Endpoints<br/>Port 8081/TCP]

        Manager --> Controller
        Manager --> MutatingWebhook
        Manager --> ValidatingWebhook
        Manager --> CertController
        Manager --> Metrics
        Manager --> Health
    end

    subgraph "Watched CRDs (KubeRay)"
        RayClusterCRD[RayCluster CRD<br/>ray.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources (per RayCluster)"
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>OpenShift]
        MTLSCerts[mTLS Certificates<br/>CA Secret]
        NetworkPol[NetworkPolicies<br/>Head + Workers]
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>External Access]
        Ingress[Kubernetes Ingress<br/>External Access]
        OAuthService[OAuth Service<br/>ClusterIP 443/TCP]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0]
        CertMgr[cert-controller<br/>v0.10.1]
        OSAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    end

    User[User/KubeRay] -->|creates| RayClusterCRD
    RayClusterCRD -->|watched by| Controller

    K8sAPI -->|calls webhook| MutatingWebhook
    K8sAPI -->|calls webhook| ValidatingWebhook

    MutatingWebhook -->|injects sidecar| OAuthProxy
    MutatingWebhook -->|injects init containers| MTLSCerts

    Controller -->|creates| OAuthProxy
    Controller -->|creates| MTLSCerts
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPol
    Controller -->|creates| Route
    Controller -->|creates| Ingress
    Controller -->|creates| OAuthService

    Controller -->|depends on| KubeRay
    CertController -->|uses| CertMgr
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OSAuth
    Controller -->|manages resources via| K8sAPI

    Metrics -->|scraped by| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>OpenShift Monitoring]

    style Manager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MutatingWebhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ValidatingWebhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayClusterCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MTLSCerts fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NetworkPol fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Route fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Ingress fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KubeRay fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertMgr fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSAuth fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
